  "prompt": "Who sings a song titled \"Home\"?",
  "response": "Several artists have released songs titled \"Home.\" Here are some of the most notable ones:\n\n1. **Edward Sharpe & the Magnetic Zeros**  \n   - **\"Home\"** (2010)  \n   This folk-rock anthem became widely popular for its catchy melody and heartfelt lyrics celebrating love and togetherness.\n\n2. **Michael Bubl\u00e9**  \n   - **\"Home\"** (2005)  \n   A soulful rendition expressing longing and the desire to be reunited with loved ones, featured on his album *It's Time*.\n\n3. **Daughtry**  \n   - **\"Home\"** (2007)  \n   A rock-infused track from their self-titled debut album, showcasing heartfelt vocals and powerful instrumentation.\n\n4. **BTS**  \n   - **\"Home\"** (2019)  \n   A song from the South Korean boy band's album that blends pop with modern sounds, delivering themes of comfort and belonging.\n\n5. **Xscape**  \n   - **\"Home\"** (1995)  \n   An R&B classic by the female group Xscape, known for its smooth harmonies and emotional depth.\n\n6. **Bebe Rexha**  \n   - **\"Home\"** (2020)  \n   A modern pop track exploring themes of self-discovery and finding one\u2019s place in the world.\n\n7. **Rebecca Ferguson**  \n   - **\"Home\"** (2013)  \n   A soulful song that highlights her powerful vocals and introspective lyrics.\n\nEach of these songs brings a unique style and interpretation to the theme of \"Home,\" so you might want to check them out to see which one resonates most with you!",
